      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Our Sincere Apologies and a Token of Appreciation for Your Patience\n\nDear [Customer Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to extend our deepest apologies for the delay in receiving your Breville Barista Pro espresso machine. We understand how frustrating it can be to wait for something as eagerly anticipated, and we are truly sorry for any inconvenience this has caused you.\n\nOur team has been working tirelessly to address the glitch in our warehouse shipping system that resulted in this delay. We assure you that we are taking all necessary steps to prevent such issues from happening in the future. As a token of our appreciation for your patience and understanding, we would like to offer you a 15% discount on your next order with us. We hope this gesture will help to make up for the inconvenience you've experienced.\n\nThank you for your continued support, and we look forward to serving you better in the future.\n\nWarm regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Your Company Name]",
