      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, that looks good. Can you make it sound a little more personal though? The customer mentioned in their complaint that they were really looking forward to using it for a brunch they are hosting this weekend, so the delay is extra annoying for them. Maybe add a line acknowledging that specific frustration?",
